file.name: oneOf.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
   title: fruity
   version: 0.0.1
paths:
   /:
      get:
         responses:
            '200':
               description: desc
               content:
                  application/json:
                     schema:
                        $ref: '#/components/schemas/fruit'
components:
   schemas:
      fruit:
         title: fruit
         properties:
            color:
               type: string
         oneOf:
            - $ref: '#/components/schemas/apple'
            - $ref: '#/components/schemas/banana'
         # additionalProperties:
         #    type: string
         # uncomment this when https://github.com/swagger-api/swagger-parser/issues/1252 is resolved
      apple:
         title: apple
         type: object
         properties:
            kind:
               type: string
      banana:
         title: banana
         type: object
         properties:
            count:
               type: number
